Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.14,0:00:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.67,0:00:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Light so glaring that it can't be hidden shatters the silence and revives in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.68,0:00:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The violently quaking and thirsty Earth stakes its life and clashes together with sparks
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.44,0:00:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just one more time is enough to create a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.66,0:00:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the power to regain the pages of memory lost in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.58,0:00:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fs30}The believing heart that penetrates the darkness searches for the place where its soul sleeps
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.88,0:00:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And burns a sharp glance of eyes that can't sparkle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.26,0:01:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two hearts of light and shadow head toward the future that the crystal reflects
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.60,0:01:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now they start to move, these eyes brimming red
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.19,0:01:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.42,0:01:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me... Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's useless trying to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.75,0:02:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You still have a mission to complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.14,0:02:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.23,0:02:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Millennium Items are now in the possession of the Pharaoh, you and Shadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.11,0:02:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shadi will surely hand over his items to the Pharaoh one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.21,0:02:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Eventually, all the Millennium Items will be in the hands of you and him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.18,0:02:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.02,0:02:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, having all seven Millennium Items
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}isn't enough to open the Door of the Underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.25,0:02:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Apart from these seven Millennium Items,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.92,0:02:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}an additional hidden item known as the Eighth Key must be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.31,0:02:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Eighth Key will open the Door of the Underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.16,0:02:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That secret is hidden in the Pharaoh's Memory World.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.92,0:02:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know nothing about all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nameless Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.76,0:02:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When the door to your memory opens...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.49,0:02:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the Ultimate Dark Game from three thousand years ago will start!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Ultimate Game"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[Year 1960]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.15,0:03:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we finally here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to turn back,\N now's the time, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.71,0:03:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From here on out is\N the territory of the {\i1}dead{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the sun goes down, darkness will soon devour everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might even eat up the souls of the living.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Valley of the Kings... This is the burial grounds of Ancient Egyptian Pharaohs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.19,0:03:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm here in search of the ultimate game.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There have been more than sixty graves discovered in this valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.26,0:03:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's said that {\i1}nobody{\i0} has been able to enter the inner chambers of the King's tomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before the World War,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:04:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a member of the British Royal Archaeological Team said this with his last breath...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'The Dark Games"... or so they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Dark Games"...\N That sure is an interesting name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.90,0:04:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That tomb has many traps that nobody could solve.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.74,0:04:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there must be wonderful treasures hidden in the depths of that tomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Sir, we've made a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are different from death-seekers like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.71,0:04:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll guide you until we reach the entrance of that tomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you will need to lead us to the treasures after that, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.61,0:04:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no interest in treasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have something to eat first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Graverobbing is best done at night, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.22,0:04:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:05:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, we've actually been wanting to ask you about your strange attire...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you planning to propose to someone in the tomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.74,0:05:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I live only for games.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.42,0:05:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I always show my greatest respect towards my gaming opponents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.23,0:05:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if I ever lose a game...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then I'll trade my tux in for denim jeans and overalls,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...while collecting {\i1}years{\i0} instead of {\i1}chips{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tonight's{\i0} game could cost you more than just the clothes on your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've traveled the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}playing cards, Chess and various other gambles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.07,0:05:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have won in countless games.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was at that time that I heard of a rumored legend...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}About the most dangerous game that exists in Egypt's Valley of the Kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There lies glory that nobody else has ever claimed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With my gaming life at stake, I take on this challenge for the ultimate honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:06:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have you go first, Mister Mutou.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bones of graverobbers...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are these the remains of the people who lost in the game?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Brother, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.58,0:06:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The treasures have appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.69,0:06:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.72,0:06:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? We are the ones that found them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the game has started.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? We've reached a dead-end!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does our journey end here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Beyond this point... rests the great Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Gods shall punish you, o ye who dares disturb him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your body will rot and your soul be cursed to eternal darkness."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can interpret hieroglyphs?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.81,0:07:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't... So I'm rather amazed myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:07:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, the real entrance is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.80,0:08:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't see an entrance anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Horus, the Falcon God,\N represents the Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.25,0:08:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Opener of The Way."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.22,0:08:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what... is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like this is one of the main stages in the game...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible for us to climb down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.89,0:08:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can only take that path.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go ahead then!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.65,0:08:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be treasures lying ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Brother, I don't want to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.99,0:08:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now listen to me! {\i1}We're{\i0} not the ones in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:09:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just need him to clear the game and then we can get to the treasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.79,0:09:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.71,0:09:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh... Don't worry. If the need arises...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.91,0:09:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The entrance..!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wall is..!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-At this rate...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So the only way out is\N through this passage?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But there's no telling what kind of traps lie ahead...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.81,0:09:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Get moving this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop hesitating!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must cross it first!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn! I've got no choice but to take this path...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.51,0:09:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to get past this many statues!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If this is truly a Dark Game...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.91,0:10:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...there must be a solution to this puzzle hidden somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if this goes on...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It stopped for a moment just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.52,0:10:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lousy fraud!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that talk about showing your greatest respect towards games?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Games?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.86,0:10:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.. That's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In Ancient Egypt, the Pharaoh is God!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.12,0:10:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And statues dedicated to the Pharaoh always have the left foot forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It symbolizes taking your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}from the left side of your chest and presenting it to your god, the Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A display of ultimate loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.71,0:10:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the area of the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.01,0:10:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter who it may be,\N all must be humble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those who forget respect are punished with death!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've solved the puzzle of this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.10,0:11:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Walk by keeping your left foot forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.19,0:11:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get attacked by the statues if you walk with your right foot forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Left foot?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard of this method of walking!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.29,0:11:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're nearly there! Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.67,0:11:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mushara!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.74,0:11:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but this is the rule of the Dark Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.62,0:11:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, keep moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the second room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The {\i1}Ka{\i0} sealed in the stone slabs shall judge you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.12,0:12:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cowardly will have their souls eaten by demons...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The courageous will be shown the way..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.38,0:12:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's got to be treasure inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.66,0:12:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like I've seen this before...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Go on already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.75,0:13:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just a bit more...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.25,0:13:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With this, I will have conquered the legendary game.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.02,0:13:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Looks like he's going to get across safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.83,0:13:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now that I know this bridge is safe, I have no further use for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You solved the Dark Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.19,0:13:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you can die in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard..!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going ahead, you odd-ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the treasure belongs to {\i1}me{\i0} now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I imagining things?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.24,0:13:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But this drawing is really mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.16,0:13:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the..?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come so far...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this... the end...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've been waiting for you, Shimon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.20,0:15:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the symbol of glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.39,0:15:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that was how I obtained the Millennium Puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, you were cool back in your day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may have exaggerated things a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why are you asking\N me about the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you planning to go to Egypt?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.30,0:15:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stone slab in the museum has been sent back to Egypt already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right... We'll embark on our journey to Egypt tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And when I show the three God Cards to the stone slab...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The other me will set off on a journey to get his memories back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Grandpa, do you still remember the location of the Pharaoh's tomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.18,0:15:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I hired special guides back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Valley of the Kings is a big place and there are many caves that look the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:15:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.48,0:15:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm going to Egypt,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to visit the place where the Millennium Puzzle originally was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.16,0:16:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't! You can't go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.20,0:16:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, Yugi, can you show me one last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again? This is the fifth time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the thought of not seeing them makes me really depressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it already, Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The God Cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want them~!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.71,0:16:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! You can't have them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.82,0:16:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It stirs my blood as a collector!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you won't sell them,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,leave them here when you go to Egypt and let me display them in the store!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No means no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, you don't understand just how important these cards are to the other me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.97,0:16:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.23,0:16:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The spirit of the Pharaoh \Nresiding in your body
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:16:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is going to embark on his journey soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've been waiting for you, Shimon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I was injured, I brought the Millennium Puzzle straight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.93,0:17:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But there may be areas in that tomb no one has ever set foot in...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And perhaps only the one who solved the Millennium Puzzle can reach those areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.63,0:17:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, the owner of the Millennium Puzzle inherits the spirit of the Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.14,0:17:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as a result, you will be tested endlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tested?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, and no matter what happens, you must not give up during those trials!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are things that can only be gained when you overcome these trials.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.08,0:17:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things that can be gained?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, things like courage and glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.63,0:17:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will understand when the time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.83,0:17:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.93,0:17:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose to these tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my grandson!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.85,0:17:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, time to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.88,0:18:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.28,0:18:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I... have some things I need to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.99,0:18:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you holding yourself back because of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding back?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Many things happened after we got the God Cards in Battle City.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I was thinking that\N maybe I was the reason
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}you've been holding off on \Nyour journey for your memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't help but think that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I met you when I completed the Millennium Puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.26,0:18:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ever since you appeared, I wasn't lonely anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.10,0:18:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I got to know Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}, Honda-{\i0}kun{\i1},
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba-{\i0}kun{\i1}, and many other friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.98,0:19:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because of you, I've gotten so many things that I'm really thankful for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I'm really sad if you're holding yourself back because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other Me, please don't hold yourself back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll be fine even if I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.61,0:19:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, Partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens to me from now on, I'll never forget you and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other Me... Just like how I put the Millennium Puzzle together...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.39,0:19:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's your turn to put the pieces of your memory back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.96,0:19:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Before you complete your mission, we'll always be partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.98,0:19:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right, Partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Yugi didn't think we would come and steal the God Cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.37,0:20:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. Now that it's come ta this, let's give it all we got!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.25,0:20:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes, he's awake! Let's run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.71,0:20:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did they go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's supposed to be my duty to protect the God Cards and the Millennium Items..!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it this far, so we can relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.27,0:20:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The God Cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.30,0:20:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The freakin' {\i1}God Cards{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell're you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.07,0:21:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally my turn to appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.62,0:21:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you! You're that guy who's always following Yugi around!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.78,0:21:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be... You're also goin' after the God Cards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.25,0:21:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be a problem for me if you went and took the God Cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll dispose of anyone who gets in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.72,0:21:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was..!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.70,0:21:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.98,0:21:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.93,0:21:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To show us now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.23,0:22:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a map isn't needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.70,0:22:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only what tore apart the darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.83,0:22:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the hope that lies in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.96,0:22:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without deciding on a goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.39,0:22:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll just take a step toward my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.02,0:22:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}EYE'S, while I feel them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.48,0:22:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll find your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.12,0:22:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh! EYE'S, if what I wished for...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.33,0:23:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...shudders my very soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.88,0:23:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.32,0:23:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to help the other Yugi start on his journey to the Memory World,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.34,0:23:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi made up his mind to go to Egypt.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.18,0:23:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0} appeared as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.30,0:23:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he our enemy? Or perhaps an ally?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.14,0:23:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got back the God Cards Haga and Ryuzaki stole...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.68,0:23:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but he suddenly announced the start of the Ultimate Dark Game.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.81,0:23:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, he goes to challenge Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} to a Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.88,0:23:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.60,0:23:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dark Bakura on the Move"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.11,0:23:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
